languages.text: "Владайм-Владайм, ты, наверное, думал, что единственный на всем Футфоле умеешь заводить друзей". {n}Джай разводит руками и снисходительно ухмыляется.{/n} "Я ведь сказала, что найду сделку получше".

traits.locale_text: "Владайм-Владайм, ты, наверное, думал, что единственный на всем Футфоле умеешь заводить друзей". {n}Джай разводит руками и снисходительно ухмыляется.{/n} "Я ведь сказала, что найду сделку получше".

languages.text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

languages.text: 「ヴラダイム、ヴラダイム…フットフォールで友達を作る方法は、自分しか知らないと思っていたのかしら」{n}ジェイは肩をすくめ、見下すように笑みを浮かべる。{/n}「もっと良い取引を見つけると言ったでしょ」
languages.original_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

languages.text: “弗拉迪姆，弗拉迪姆，你肯定以为你是落脚港唯一一个懂得如何交朋友的人吧？”{n}婕伊耸了耸肩，居高临下地笑了起来。{/n}“我早就告诉过你，我会找到更合适的买卖。”
languages.original_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

languages.text: «Vladaym, Vladaym. ¿Qué se cree? ¿Que es el único en todo Paso que sabe hacer amigos?». {n}Jae se encoge de hombros y sonríe con condescendencia.{/n} «Le advertí de que encontraría un trato más interesante».
languages.original_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

traits.locale_text: «Vladaym, Vladaym. ¿Qué se cree? ¿Que es el único en todo Paso que sabe hacer amigos?». {n}Jae se encoge de hombros y sonríe con condescendencia.{/n} «Le advertí de que encontraría un trato más interesante».

languages.text: « Vladaym, Vladaym... Vous pensiez vraiment être la seule personne à Castel capable de se faire des amis ? » {n}Jae hausse les épaules et lui lance un sourire narquois.{/n} « Je vous avais pourtant dit que je me trouverais un meilleur accord. »
languages.original_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

languages.text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, Ihr dachtet wohl, Ihr wärt der Einzige auf Footfall, der weiß, wie man Freundschaften schließt. {n}Jae zuckt mit den Schultern und lächelt herablassend.{/n} Ich sagte doch, ich finde ein besseres Geschäft."
languages.original_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

languages.text: "Vladaym, Vladaym. Binliman'da arkadaş edinmeyi bilen bir tek sen değilsin ya." {n}Jae, omuz silkip küçümsemeyle sırıtıyor.{/n} "Bana anlaşma mı yok, demiştim sana."
languages.original_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym, you must have thought you were the only one on Footfall who knew how to make friends." {n}Jae shrugs and smirks condescendingly.{/n} "Told you I'd find a better deal."

traits.locale_text: "Vladaym, Vladaym... Binliman'da arkadaş edinmeyi bilen tek kişi sen değilsin ya..." {n}Jae omuz silkip küçümsemeyle sırıtıyor.{/n} "Daha iyisini bulurum demiştim sana."
